


What happens in the case of binary search if the array is not sorted?

It will not be applied on unsorted list as it only works on sorted list. Instead, one needs to use the linear search to have it work. 

What is the purpose of constructor argument validity checking?

The ideal is to fail as soon as possible if the error occurs.

What is the purpose of using the keyword final with variables and arguments?

The purpose is that programmers should know that they should not change the value of the variable. 

What are alternatives to using Optional and how do they compare?

Null is an alternatives to using Optional. However, Optional is better to use. 